Manage runtime profiles, provider accounts, model aliases,
tools, knowledge sources, routing policies, and spend policies.

Usage:
  agentclash infra [command]

Available Commands:
  knowledge-source Manage knowledge-sources
  model-alias      Manage model-aliases
  model-catalog    Browse the global model catalog
  provider-account Manage provider-accounts
  routing-policy   Manage routing-policies
  runtime-profile  Manage runtime-profiles
  spend-policy     Manage spend-policies
  tool             Manage tools

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for infra

Global Flags:
      --api-url string     API base URL (overrides config)
      --json               Output in JSON format
      --no-color           Disable color output
      --non-interactive    Disable interactive prompts (also honored: CI=true, AGENTCLASH_NON_INTERACTIVE=1, --json, no TTY)
  -o, --output string      Output format: table, json, yaml
  -q, --quiet              Suppress non-essential output
  -v, --verbose            Enable debug output on stderr
  -w, --workspace string   Workspace ID (overrides config)
      --yes                Skip confirmation prompts

Use "agentclash infra [command] --help" for more information about a command.
